<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="clothing-n">clothing <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kləʊðɪŋ/    美 /'kloʊðɪŋ/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>衣服；服装：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>No matter where we are, we always have food, clothing, and shelter as well as people who love us.
无论身在何处，我们都能得到食物、衣服和住处，还有关爱我们的人。</p></div>

<h3 id="clothing-clothes">辨析 clothing, clothes</h3>
<p>二者都指“衣服”。<br />
<strong>clothing</strong> 是服装的统称，泛指服装或某类衣服。指服装的制作或销售时要用clothing，为不可数名词。日常口语中不常用。
<strong>clothes</strong> 指穿的衣服，只用作复数。</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a suit of clothes
一套衣服（包括上衣、背心和裤子等）</p></div></div>